<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/128.0.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="24.7.13"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="_rRZovGLQm-gsCpOWQ8V"> <mxGraphModel dx="17058" dy="7912" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
actor User
actor Finder as Finder
actor Loser as Loser
actor Admin

usecase \"Sign Up\" as UC1
usecase \"Log In\" as UC2
usecase \"Select Found or Lost\" as UC3
usecase \"Report Found Document\" as UC4
usecase \"Search Lost Document\" as UC5
usecase \"Validate Documents\" as UC6
usecase \"Verify Match and Confirm\" as UC7
usecase \"Pay to View Contact\" as UC8
usecase \"Access Chat System\" as UC9
usecase \"Claim Reward\" as UC10
usecase \"Multiple Identifier Verification\" as UC11
usecase \"In-Person Verification at HQ\" as UC12
usecase \"System Administration\" as UC13

User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
Finder --> UC4
Loser --> UC5
UC4 --> UC6
UC5 --> UC7 : \"Enter Unique Identifiers (ID, License, UPI)\"
UC7 --> UC8 : \"Confirm Match\"
UC8 --> UC9 : \"Payment via MTN MoMo API\"
UC9 --> UC10 : \"Finder Claims Reward\"
UC7 --> UC11 : \"Multiple Identifiers (DOB, Place of Issue, Photo)\"
UC11 --> UC8 : \"Match Verified and Pay\"
UC7 --> UC12 : \"No Identifiers Known\"
Admin --> UC13
@enduml
",
 "format": "svg"
}" id="hWBbNlQ9A2H0gAgvvFjt-1"> <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry x="-11050" y="-5415.35" width="5222.14" height="3211.38" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> </UserObject> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
start
:Sign Up;
:Log In;
if (Found or Lost?) then (Found)
 :Select Found;
 :Check Boxes of Found Items;
 :Take Pictures;
 :Scan Validity (Rwanda);
 if (Documents Valid?) then (Yes)
 :Store Found Items;
 else (No)
 :Notify Finder Invalid Items;
 endif
else (Lost)
 :Select Lost;
 :Search Lost Items by Name/ID;
 if (Knows Unique Identifier?) then (Yes)
 :Enter ID, License No., or UPI;
 :Search for Matches;
 else (No)
 :Enter DOB, Place of Issue, and Upload Photo;
 :Verify Match with System;
 endif
 if (Matches Found?) then (Yes)
 :View Matched Items;
 if (Verified or Identified?) then (Yes)
 :Proceed to Payment;
 :Pay via MTN MoMo API;
 if (Payment Success?) then (Yes)
 :Access Chat System;
 :Exchange Contacts & Locations;
 :Prompt Finder to Claim Reward;
 :Transfer Reward to Finder;
 else (No)
 :Notify Loser - Payment Failed;
 endif
 else (No)
 :Notify Loser - No Confirmation;
 endif
 else (No)
 :Notify Loser - No Match;
 endif
endif
stop
@enduml
",
 "format": "svg"
}" id="hWBbNlQ9A2H0gAgvvFjt-2"> <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry x="-5827.86" y="-5410" width="4475.18" height="3946.19" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> </UserObject> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
actor User
participant \"Lost and Found System\" as System
participant \"MTN API\" as MTN

User -> System: Sign Up
System -> User: Request Valid Phone Number
User -> System: Enter Phone Number
System -> User: Log In
User -> System: Choose (Found or Lost)

alt Found
 User -> System: Report Found Items
 System -> User: Request Pictures
 User -> System: Upload Pictures
 System -> System: Validate Items
 System -> User: Store Valid Found Items
else Lost
 User -> System: Search Lost Items
 alt Knows Identifier
 User -> System: Enter ID, License, or UPI
 System -> System: Search for Matches
 else No Identifier
 User -> System: Enter DOB, Place of Issue, Upload Photo
 System -> System: Verify with Multiple Identifiers
 end
 alt Match Found
 System -> User: Display Matched Items
 User -> System: Confirm Match
 alt Match Confirmed
 User -> System: Proceed to Payment
 System -> MTN: Request Payment
 MTN -> System: Payment Confirmation
 System -> User: Access Chat System
 User -> System: Exchange Contacts
 User -> System: Confirm Retrieval
 System -> System: Transfer Reward to Finder
 else Match Not Confirmed
 System -> User: No Further Action
 end
 else No Match
 System -> User: Notify No Matches
 end
end

alt No Identifiers Known
 User -> System: Request In-Person Verification at HQ
 System -> User: Direct to HQ
end

@enduml
",
 "format": "svg"
}" id="hWBbNlQ9A2H0gAgvvFjt-7"> <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry x="-1352.68" y="-5420" width="2202.68" height="4201.68" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> </UserObject> </root> </mxGraphModel> </diagram> </mxfile>
